data.value:
Project Home: https://bitbucket.org/elmassivo/gcn-usb-adapter/
Written in C#, this program feeds data to vJoy (a virtual joystick application) from a LibUsbDotNet HID driver.
The latest LibUsbDotNet can be found here: http://sourceforge.net/projects/libusbdotnet/
The latest vJoy can be found here: http://vjoystick.sourceforge.net/site/
